elopment: ideation/conception, formulation, ingredient selection, packaging and manufacturing</li><li class="li1">Generate ideas for new products, concepts and innovative NPD methods</li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Lead collaboration and communication with our suppliers and their R&amp;D departments</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Scout trends (Beauty, Lifestyle, Fashion), customer research, social media, market, competitor analysis and cosmetics publications<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Optimize existing formulations for performance, internal/regulatory compliance and formula quality</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Collaborate closely with departments of brand strategy &amp; marketing</span></li></ul><p class="p2"><span class="s1"></span><br></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>Your profile</b></span></p><ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Excellent degree in cosmetic science, biochemistry, chemistry, chemical engineering or related fields</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Ideally first professional experiences in product development in the beauty industry</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Passion and knowledge in the clean &amp; natural cosmetics market/consumer insights</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Both analytical and creative capabilities</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Growth mindset and can-do mentality</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Sense of beauty, sustainable and vegan lifestyle</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Excellent communication skills (written and verbal)</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Good handling skills of MS Office products (esp. Excel) and Google Drive (Docs, Sheets, and Slides)</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Proficiency in English is required; German/Italian/French is a plus</span></li></ul><p class="p2"><span class="s1"></span><br></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>Your benefits</b></span></p><p></p><ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Join an international, fast growing start-up with flat hierarchies, short decision-making path and room to actively shape the company</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Be part of an ambitious and empowering team that strongly focuses on sustainability and disrupting the industry<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">A culture of trust, empowerment and constructive feedback in a positive and inspiring work atmosphere</span></li><li class="li1"><span class="s2"></span><span class="s1">Enjoy our spacious and central Berlin office and the flexibility to integrate remote working hours<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></li></ul><div><p class="p1"><span class="s1"><br></span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Sounds like a fit?</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Please send your CV, salary expectations and your earliest possible starting date to <u><a href="mailto:people@gitti.de" class="">people@gitti.de</a></u>. The beauty industry is changing fast, support us to re-invent it.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">We cannot wait to meet you!</span></p><p class="p2"><span class="s1"><i></i></span><br></p><p class="p1"></p><p class="p3"><span class="s1"><i>“variety is the spice of life” — and a celebrated component of our culture. At gitti, we strive to create an inclusive environment that empowers our employees. We believe that our products benefit from our diverse backgrounds and experiences and are proud to be an equal opportunity employer: all qualified applicants are considered for positions regardless of race, ethnic origin, gender, age, religion or belief, marital status, gender identification, sexual orientation, or disability.</i></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit-->
